node.text:
Up your sandwich game with this Italian Chicken Schnitzel Sando!

INGREDIENTS
Chicken
* 	2 chicken breast, butterflied and pounded thin
* 	2 lemons, juiced 
* 	2 tbsp olive oil
* 	3 minced garlic cloves
* 	½ tsp Chilli flakes 
* 	2 bay leaves
* 	3 thyme sprigs 
* 	A few roughly torn sage leaves
* 	2 sprigs osemary
* 	Salt and pepper
* 	1 egg, beaten
* 	½ cup panko
* 	½ cup fine breadcrumbs
 
Slaw
* 	½ White cabbage 
* 	½ White onion, thinly sliced
* 	1 tbsp Honey 
* 	2 Lemons, juiced
* 	Salt and pepper to taste
 
Salsa verde
* 	30g Parsley, finely chopped
* 	1 tbsp Capers, chopped
* 	½ red onion, finely chopped
* 	½ red chilli, finely chopped
* 	½ tsp Dijon
* 	3 tbsp Red wine vinegar 
* 	2 tbsp Olive oil 
* 	1 Anchovy
 
Artichoke Aioli
* 	1 egg yolk
* 	1 garlic clove
* 	1 tsp dijon mustard
* 	Pinch salt
* 	2 artichoke hearts 
* 	1 lemon, juiced
* 	Vegetable oil - around 100ml
 
To serve
* 	Thick white bread

CROQUE MONSIEUR CROISSANT LASAGNA

INGREDIENTS
* 	10 shop-bought all-butter croissants
* 	a little butter for greasing
* 	1 1/2 cups bechamel sauce
* 	2 cups grated emmental cheese
* 	10 slices wafer thin cooked ham, plus a little more for layering
* 	nutmeg, a scrape
* 	dijon mustard, 1/2 tsp per croissant

node.text:
We're not being corn-y but this corn dog may be the best you've ever had! Chicken Fajita Corndog
* 	3 chicken breasts, cut into large chunks
* 	2 tbsp smoked paprika
* 	1 tbsp cumin powder
* 	1 tsp coriander powder
* 	1 tsp onion granules
* 	1/2 tsp garlic granules
* 	1/2 tsp cayenne pepper
* 	1 tsp salt
* 	240g cornmeal
* 	150g plain flour
* 	1 tbsp baking powder
* 	1 tbsp taco seasoning
* 	1 tsp cayenne
* 	1 tsp salt
* 	1 egg
* 	1 tbsp vegetable oil
* 	375ml whole milk
* 	75ml milk
* 	200ml evaporated milk
* 	175g yellow cheddar, grated
* 	1/2 tbsp hot sauce
* 	1 tbsp cornflour
#twistedfood #mealideas #dinnerideas #snack #midnightsnack #fajita  #foodfusion #hotdog

This recipe is a great arm hug in a pot! CRISPY CHICKEN WITH CREAMY BACON & MUSHROOM PASTA

INGREDIENTS
 3 chicken breasts
1 ½ cups plain flour
½ cup grated parmesan 
½ tsp garlic powder
1 tsp salt
1 tsp pepper
2 tbsp chopped parsley
2 cups buttermilk
2 eggs, whisked
 
8 rashers bacon, chopped
1 tbsp butter
1 onion, diced
3 cloves garlic, minced
2 cups, sliced mushrooms
½ cup chicken stock
3 cups heavy cream
4 cups baby spinach
½ cup grated parmesan cheese
400g cooked linguine
Salt and pepper to taste

Cheese Stuffed Chicken Parmesan Meatballs
INGREDIENTS
500g chicken mince 
1 egg beaten
½ cup fresh breadcrumbs
½ cup finely grated parmesan cheese
2 tbsp chopped parsley 
2 cloves garlic, minced
Salt and pepper
 
Sliced ham
Cubed swiss cheese
 
2 tsp oil
40g butter
2 cloves garlic, minced
40g plain flour
2 cups chicken stock
1 cup heavy cream
1 tsp dijon mustard
400g penne pasta, cooked
1 cup grated cheddar cheese, divided
1 cup grated swiss cheese, divided

Pizza

node.text:
Up your sandwich game with this Italian Chicken Schnitzel Sando!

INGREDIENTS
Chicken
* 	2 chicken breast, butterflied and pounded thin
* 	2 lemons, juiced 
* 	2 tbsp olive oil
* 	3 minced garlic cloves
* 	½ tsp Chilli flakes 
* 	2 bay leaves
* 	3 thyme sprigs 
* 	A few roughly torn sage leaves
* 	2 sprigs osemary
* 	Salt and pepper
* 	1 egg, beaten
* 	½ cup panko
* 	½ cup fine breadcrumbs
 
Slaw
* 	½ White cabbage 
* 	½ White onion, thinly sliced
* 	1 tbsp Honey 
* 	2 Lemons, juiced
* 	Salt and pepper to taste
 
Salsa verde
* 	30g Parsley, finely chopped
* 	1 tbsp Capers, chopped
* 	½ red onion, finely chopped
* 	½ red chilli, finely chopped
* 	½ tsp Dijon
* 	3 tbsp Red wine vinegar 
* 	2 tbsp Olive oil 
* 	1 Anchovy
 
Artichoke Aioli
* 	1 egg yolk
* 	1 garlic clove
* 	1 tsp dijon mustard
* 	Pinch salt
* 	2 artichoke hearts 
* 	1 lemon, juiced
* 	Vegetable oil - around 100ml
 
To serve
* 	Thick white bread 

#fschnitzel #foodpics #foodphotography #foodgram #foodlovers #fooddiary #foodforthought #sandwich #eeeeeats #cheesetoastie #noleftovers #foodgasm

Good news Gravy lovers - Gravy season is back! 

Cheesy beef loaded fries
Ingredients
* 1 tbsp oil
* 2.2 lb sirloin steak, cut into thin strips
* 3 tbsp flour
* 1 tbsp salt
* 1 tbsp pepper
* 1 onion, sliced roughly
* 1 tbsp tomato puree
* 2 cups beef stock
* 1 cup wine
* Thyme

HOT ROAST CHICKEN GRAVY BUNS
INGREDIENTS
* 	1 small chicken
* 	1/2 lemon
* 	1/2 bulb garlic
* 	1 1/2 tsps salt
* 	1 cup mayonnaise
* 	toasted buns, to serve
* 	1 cup chicken stock
* 	fries, to serve
* 	1 glass white wine
* 	1 tbsp french mustard
* 	1 hpd tsp plain flour

GRAVY AND MASH BOMBS
INGREDIENTS
* 	1 cup/250ml gravy
* 	3 cups/1 kilo pork mince
* 	1 tbsp chopped chives
* 	2 tbsp chopped parsley
* 	1 tbsp salt
* 	1 tsp pepper
* 	1 tsp nutmeg
* 	2 cups mashed potato
* 	1 cup plain flour
* 	4 eggs, beaten with a little milk
* 	2 cups panko breadcrumbs
* 	Groundnut oil for deep frying

Cheese stuffed mash beef Pie

* 2 1/4 lb Stewing beef
* 2 cloves Garlic
* 2 Onions
* 1 1/2 cups Beef stock
* 3 tbsp Flour
* 2 tsp Pepper
* 2 tsp Salt
* 1 tbsp Vegetable oil
* 1 tbsp Butter
* 1 small block Cheddar
* 2 cups Red wine
* 3 cups Leftover mash
* 1 tbsp Passasta

#twistedfood #recipe #pie #mash  #gravy #gravytrain #yummy #dinnerideas #nowimhungry
